---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="fraisier - Deployment Orchestrator | FraiseQL"
  description="Production deployment orchestrator for FraiseQL. Reference implementation for zero-downtime deploys with blue/green strategies and multi-database support."
>
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>🚀 fraisier</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666;">
      <strong>Deployment Orchestrator</strong> – Production-ready reference
    </p>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>What It Does</h2>
      <p>
        fraisier is the canonical reference implementation for deploying FraiseQL services to production.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Zero-downtime deploys</strong>: Blue/green strategy with automatic failover
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Multi-database support</strong>: Coordinate migrations + server updates
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Health checks</strong>: Automated validation before switching
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Kubernetes ready</strong>: Helm charts and manifests included
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Rollback capability</strong>: Instant revert on failure
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Why It Exists</h2>
      <p>
        Deploying compiled GraphQL services safely requires coordinating:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Schema compilation and validation</li>
        <li>Database migrations (using confiture)</li>
        <li>Server updates</li>
        <li>Health verification</li>
        <li>Automatic rollback on failure</li>
      </ul>
      <p>fraisier orchestrates this entire workflow automatically.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Blue/Green Deployment</strong>: Two production environments for safe switching
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Integrated Migrations</strong>: confiture handles database changes
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Health Validation</strong>: Queries run against deployed schema
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Automatic Rollback</strong>: Revert on health check failure
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Kubernetes Support</strong>: Native K8s deployments
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Multi-Database Coordination</strong>: PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, SQL Server
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Language</strong>: Rust (orchestration logic)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Infrastructure</strong>: Kubernetes, Docker, Cloud platforms
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Integrations</strong>: confiture, fraiseql-cli, health checks
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Integration with Other Tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>confiture</strong>: Orchestrates database migrations during deploy
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>fraiseql</strong>: Deploys compiled schema and server
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>fraiseql-wire</strong>: Handles streaming responses during health checks
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Quick Start</h2>
      <pre><code>{`# Deploy with blue/green strategy
fraisier deploy --schema schema.compiled.json --database postgres \\
  --blue-env production-blue \\
  --green-env production-green \\
  --health-query "query { __typename }"

# Automatic rollback if health check fails
# Switches traffic to new environment on success`}</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>GitHub Repository</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraisier" target="_blank">
          Visit fraisier on GitHub →
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Related Tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/ecosystem/fraiseql-core">fraiseql</a> – Core engine</li>
        <li><a href="/ecosystem/confiture">confiture</a> – Migrations</li>
        <li><a href="/ecosystem">← Back to Ecosystem</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
